<h1 itemprop="headline">Ex-Wall Street chieftains living large in post-meltdown world</h1>
<div class="field field-name-field-deck field-type-text-long field-label-hidden">
    <div class="field-items">
          <div class="field-item even"><h2>After the Meltdown: Part one in our series looking at the impact of the financial crisis of 2008 </h2></div>
      </div>
</div>



<div class="field field-name-field-authors field-type-relation field-label-hidden">
    
  <h4 class="authors">By <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><span class="author"><span rel="author" itemprop="name"><a href="http://www.publicintegrity.org/authors/alison-fitzgerald" itemprop="url" title="Alison Fitzgerald">Alison Fitzgerald</a></span><a href="https://twitter.com/intent/user?screen_name=alifitzg" class="byline-twitter" title="Follow @alifitzg on Twitter"><img src="/sites/publici/themes/publici_theme/images/icons/twitter/author-byline-bird.png" width="15" height="10" /></a><a href="/node/12607/rss" class="byline-rss" title="Alison Fitzgerald RSS feed"><img src="/sites/publici/themes/publici_theme/images/icons/author-byline-rss.png" width="11" height="10" /></a><a href="mailto:afitzgerald@publicintegrity.org" class="byline-email" title="E-mail Alison Fitzgerald">email</a></span></span></h4>  <h4 class="pubdate"><time datetime="2013-09-10T06:00:00-04:00" pubdate itemprop="datePublished">6:00 am, September 10, 2013</time>&nbsp;<span class="updated">Updated: <time datetime="2013-09-16T13:50:21-04:00" pubdate itemprop="dateModified">1:50 pm, September 16, 2013</time></span></h4>
